OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1774285870
OL,3,CSteel strategy announced in bid to
OL,4,Cboost UK production
OL,6,FThe UK Government has announced an
OL,7,Fambition for up to 50% of steel used
OL,8,Fin the UK to be made in this country.
OL,10,FMinisters said the move, boosting
OL,11,Fproduction from 30%, would be coupled
OL,12,Fwith reductions in steel import quotas
OL,13,Fas part of new trade measures to
OL,14,Fpreserve steel production for critical
OL,15,Fnational infrastructure and defence.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
