FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1774285870
OL,3,CSteel strategy announced in bid to
OL,4,Cboost UK production
OL,6,FBusiness and Trade Secretary Peter
OL,7,FKyle gave details of the strategy
OL,8,Fwhile on a visit to Tata Steel's plant
OL,9,Fin Port Talbot. Work building a new
OL,10,FElectric Arc Furnace (EAF), replacing
OL,11,Fthe two blast furnaces, began last
OL,12,Fyear at the south Wales site.
OL,14,FFrom July, overall quota levels for
OL,15,Fsteel imports will be reduced by 60%
OL,16,Fcompared to current arrangements, and
OL,17,Fsteel coming into the UK above these
OL,18,Flevels will be subject to a 50% tariff.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1774285870
OL,3,CSteel strategy announced in bid to
OL,4,Cboost UK production
OL,6,FMinisters said this would ensure the
OL,7,FUK steel sector's future in the face
OL,8,Fof global overcapacity.
OL,10,FThe National Wealth Fund will be the
OL,11,Fmain mechanism for providing up to
OL,12,F#2.5 billion of financing for
OL,13,Finvestment in the steel sector this
OL,14,FParliament.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1774285870
OL,3,CSteel strategy announced in bid to
OL,4,Cboost UK production
OL,6,FBusiness and Trade Secretary Peter
OL,7,FKyle said action was needed because
OL,8,Fwithout it, the UK's steelmaking
OL,9,Fcapability faces "real jeopardy",
OL,10,Fleaving the country reliant on
OL,11,Foverseas suppliers for materials
OL,12,Fessential to energy security, defence
OL,13,Fand transport infrastructure.
OL,15,FMr Kyle said: "Making steel in the UK
OL,16,Fis vital for national security,
OL,17,Fcritical infrastructure and the wider
OL,18,Feconomy.
OL,26,@qD@ROUqD@`O]wD@OOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/13
