OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1774285870
OL,3,CSteel strategy announced in bid to
OL,4,Cboost UK production
OL,6,F"Steel-making is a cornerstone of our
OL,7,Fmodern industrial policy that
OL,8,Fdeliberately focuses support for key
OL,9,Findustries, technologies, and
OL,10,Fstrategically important sectors.
OL,12,F"With this strategy we are closing the
OL,13,Fdecades-long chapter of destructive de-
OL,14,Findustrialisation and committing
OL,15,Finstead to strengthening and
OL,16,Fsustaining Britain as a steel-making
OL,17,Fnation."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1774285870
OL,3,CSteel strategy announced in bid to
OL,4,Cboost UK production
OL,6,FMr Kyle said the Government's ambition
OL,7,Fwas to boost domestic production so
OL,8,Fthat it can meet up to 50% of domestic
OL,9,Fdemand for steel, and secure the
OL,10,Findustry's role in supporting vital UK
OL,11,Fsectors such as infrastructure,
OL,12,Fdefence and clean energy.
OL,14,FThe strategy confirms electric arc
OL,15,Ffurnaces (EAF) as the future of
OL,16,FBritish steelmaking, continuing the
OL,17,Fshift from blast furnaces to cleaner,
OL,18,FEAF-based production using recycled
OL,19,Fscrap to support net zero.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1774285870
OL,3,CSteel strategy announced in bid to
OL,4,Cboost UK production
OL,6,FThe shift has led to job losses in
OL,7,Fsteel plants including the site in
OL,8,FPort Talbot, where thousands of staff
OL,9,Fhave been impacted. A #1.25bn EAF is
OL,10,Fcurrently being built in the town,
OL,11,Fwhich is set to be up and running by
OL,12,Fthe end of 2027.
OL,14,FIt is thought that it will be one of
OL,15,Fthe largest furnaces of its kind in
OL,16,Fthe world, melting mostly scrap steel
OL,17,Fto produce three million tonnes of
OL,18,Fsteel per year.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1774285870
OL,3,CSteel strategy announced in bid to
OL,4,Cboost UK production
OL,6,FReacting to the announcement, First
OL,7,FMinister Eluned Morgan said: "Steel
OL,8,Fhas a long and proud history here in
OL,9,FWales, where the industry is the
OL,10,Flifeblood of many communities.
OL,12,F"The publication of the UK
OL,13,FGovernment's Steel Strategy is good
OL,14,Fnews for our steel communities and the
OL,15,Fthousands of people across Wales who
OL,16,Fwork in or around the industry, now
OL,17,Fand in the future.
OL,26,@oD@^OUtD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1774285870
OL,3,CSteel strategy announced in bid to
OL,4,Cboost UK production
OL,6,F"The commitment for 50% of steel used
OL,7,Fin the UK to be made here is
OL,8,Fimportant, not just for steelworkers
OL,9,Fbut to the Welsh economy as a whole.
OL,11,F"The strategy also reaffirms the
OL,12,Ftransition to electric arc steel
OL,13,Fproduction in the UK, where Port
OL,14,FTalbot is leading the way, not just in
OL,15,Fthe UK, but across Europe. It was
OL,16,Fgreat to be able to meet the Tata
OL,17,Fmanagement and unions again and to see
OL,18,Fthe progress that has been made in
OL,19,Fbuilding the new electric arc steel
OL,20,Fplant."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU|D@GO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1774285870
OL,3,CSteel strategy announced in bid to
OL,4,Cboost UK production
OL,6,FGareth Stace, director general of UK
OL,7,FSteel, said: "This is a significant
OL,8,Fmoment, and Government ministers
OL,9,Fdeserve recognition for their
OL,10,Fleadership today.
OL,12,F"The Government's bravery in taking
OL,13,Fthe required measures represents a
OL,14,Freal shift in the culture of
OL,15,FWestminster from protecting the
OL,16,Fideology of free trade at any cost, to
OL,17,Fdefending critical industries and
OL,18,Fnational security."
OL,26,@oD@NOUtD@AOUzD@SO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
