OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1774285870
OL,3,CSteel strategy announced in bid to
OL,4,Cboost UK production
OL,6,FSecretary of State for Wales Jo
OL,7,FStevens said: "The UK Government is
OL,8,Fstanding up for Welsh steelmaking and
OL,9,Fshowing that we will do whatever it
OL,10,Ftakes to boost domestic steel
OL,11,Fproduction and protect the thousands
OL,12,Fof steelmaking jobs in our communities.
OL,14,F"Welsh steel is expected to account
OL,15,Ffor half of future UK steelmaking. It
OL,16,Fis not only a vital part of the South
OL,17,FWales economy, but also a crucial part
OL,18,Fof the UK's industrial strategy,
OL,19,Finfrastructure capabilities and
OL,20,Fnational security.
OL,26,@oD@OOUvD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1774285870
OL,3,CSteel strategy announced in bid to
OL,4,Cboost UK production
OL,6,F"We said we would back our
OL,7,Fsteelworkers and steel communities and
OL,8,Fwe are delivering on that promise `
OL,9,FWelsh steelmaking now has a secure and
OL,10,Fbright future."
OL,12,FCharlotte Brumpton-Childs, GMB
OL,13,Fnational secretary, said: "GMB had
OL,14,Fbeen calling for a steel strategy for
OL,15,Fa long time, so it's good we now have
OL,16,Fsome kind of plan.
OL,18,F"This administration has done more for
OL,19,FUK steel than any government for many,
OL,20,Fmany years.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@OO]uD@[OUzD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1774285870
OL,3,CSteel strategy announced in bid to
OL,4,Cboost UK production
OL,6,F"But, as ever, the devil will be in
OL,7,Fthe detail and key questions around
OL,8,Fownership of Scunthorpe and the future
OL,9,Ftechnology mix will be key to our
OL,10,Fmembers and their livelihoods."
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
